Install WSL
  https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/wsl/install-win10
  - Used Ubuntu from Windows store

Slowness on WSL due to Windows Defender
  - Exclude entire WSL subtree
  Virus & threat protection settings > Add or remove exclusions
    Add: %LOCALAPPDATA%\Packages\CanonicalGroupLimited...

Install termainl emulator
  https://github.com/mintty/wsltty/releases
  - Installed version 1.9.6

Update Ubuntu files
  sudo apt-get udpate
  sudo apt-get upgrade

Shortcut to wsltty
  Target: C:\Users\andre\AppData\Local\wsltty\bin\mintty.exe --WSL= --configdir="C:\Users\andre\AppData\Roaming\wsltty" -~ 
  Start in: %USERPROFILE%

Copy/Paste with windows
  - Install VcXsrv
  - Add to startup programs

Edit with Vim in Windows Explorer
  https://nickjanetakis.com/blog/launching-wsl-programs-from-a-right-click-windows-menu
  In registry
    - Computer
      - HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT
        - *
          - shell
            - Vim
                Value name: (Default)
                  Value data: Edit with Vim
                Value name: Icon
                  Value data: C:\Users\andre\Pictures\vim.ico
              - command
                  Value name: (Default)
                    Value data: C:\Users\andre\AppData\Local\wsltty\bin\mintty.exe --WSL= --configdir="C:\Users\andre\AppData\Roaming\wsltty" -t "%1" -e bash --login -c "vim \"$(wslpath '%1')\""

